HEADWORD: jingoist
<hw>jin"go*ist</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who is
jingoistic; a bellicose patriot; an extreme bellicose nationalist; an
aggressive chauvinist.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> chauvinist, jingo, flag-waver,
hundred-percenter.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source> + <source>PJC</source>]</p>

